  "description": "Both voices on Phase Distortion (CZ-style) in LOVE at +0.65. Voice 1 depth at 0.72 produces a resonant formant near 2400 Hz — the first vowel 'ah'. Voice 2 depth at 0.38 sits at a lower formant — 'oh'. Through LOVE, the two vowels fuse into a choir-like texture that no single oscillator can achieve. Resonance at 0.3 on both filters adds the Formant Whisper.",
